CONTROL:
LEFT and RIGHT arrow keys to move a block in EDIT MODE              *
LEFT and RIGHT arrow keys to move timeframe in DISPLAY MODE         *
UP and DOWN arrow keys to change active field of block in EDIT MODE 
UP and DOWN arrow keys to change move level frame in DISPLAY MODE   *
PLUS and MINUS keys to extend timeframe in DISPLAY MODE             *
PLUS and MINUS keys to resize block in EDIT MODE                    *
DELETE key to remove block in EDIT MODE                             *
EQUALITY key to resize timeframe to fit blocks in DISPLAY MODE      *
